    <title>Sorcerer Changes (by Nuke)</title>
    <link>https://forum.throneoflies.com/t/sorcerer-changes-by-nuke/74470</link>
    <description>&gt; # Sorcerer
&gt; **Neutral Killer**
&gt; Passive 1: Magic Armor - Immune to death and bleeding
&gt; Passive 2: Perception - If you would try to attack someone who would survive the attack then you will instead learn their class and visitors. You won&#39;t attack them if this triggers
&gt;
&gt; Day Ability 1: Hex - Plant a hex on target player. You may have as many hex as you want active at the same time. If you select someone who has a hex you will remove the hex and can use 1 additional day ability (max of 2). Cannot place a hex on the King (Unlimited)
&gt; Day Ability 2: Curse - Target player cannot be healed and loses death immunity tonight (3 uses)
&gt;
&gt; Night Ability 1: Magic Missile - Kill target player (Unlimited)
&gt; Night Ability 2: Ritual - Kill all players with a hex on them. Does not count as an attack (Unlimited)

Note: Ritual does not bypass death immunity without Curse 

Curse can target King</description>
    
